# node
node_modules/

# Lockfile intentionally not committed: the Rolldown native-binding bug
# (https://github.com/npm/cli/issues/4828) means npm prunes optional deps
# for non-host platforms from the lockfile, which breaks Linux CI when the
# lockfile was generated on macOS (and vice versa). For a static docs site,
# determinism at build time is not worth shipping broken CI — we resolve
# fresh on every deploy. Switch to pnpm/bun later if we want determinism back.
package-lock.json

